1372#ifndef GLEXT_64_TYPES_DEFINED
1373/* This code block is duplicated in glxext.h, so must be protected */
1374#define GLEXT_64_TYPES_DEFINED
1375/* Define int32_t, int64_t, and uint64_t types for UST/MSC */
1376/* (as used in the GL_EXT_timer_query extension). */
1377#if defined(__STDC_VERSION__) && __STDC_VERSION__ >= 199901L
1378#include <inttypes.h>
1379#elif defined(__sun__) || defined(__digital__)
1380#include <inttypes.h>
1381#if defined(__STDC__)
1382#if defined(__arch64__) || defined(_LP64)
1383typedef long int int64_t;
1384typedef unsigned long int uint64_t;
1385#else
1386typedef long long int int64_t;
1387typedef unsigned long long int uint64_t;
1388#endif /* __arch64__ */
1389#endif /* __STDC__ */
1390#elif defined( __VMS ) || defined(__sgi)
1391#include <inttypes.h>
1392#elif defined(__SCO__) || defined(__USLC__)
1393#include <stdint.h>
1394#elif defined(__UNIXOS2__) || defined(__SOL64__)
1395typedef long int int32_t;
1396typedef long long int int64_t;
1397typedef unsigned long long int uint64_t;
1398#elif defined(_WIN32) && defined(__GNUC__)
1399#include <stdint.h>
1400#elif defined(_WIN32)
1401typedef __int32 int32_t;
1402typedef __int64 int64_t;
1403typedef unsigned __int64 uint64_t;
1404#else
1405/* Fallback if nothing above works */
1406#include <inttypes.h>
1407#endif
1408#endif
1409typedef uint64_t GLuint64;
1410typedef int64_t GLint64;
